247	
248	### Entity: CycleEntry
249	
250	| Field | Type | Required | Description |
251	|---|---|---|---|
252	| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |
253	| `startDate` | `DateTime` | Yes | First day of period |
254	| `endDate` | `DateTime` | No | Last day of period (can be inferred) |
255	| `cycleLength` | `int` | No | Manual override for cycle length |
256	| `notes` | `String` | No | User notes about this cycle |
257	| `isIrregular` | `bool` | No | Flag for irregular patterns |
258	
259	### Provider: CycleEntryProvider
260	
261	**State:**
262	- `entries: List<CycleEntry>` — all logged cycles
263	- `averageCycleLength: int` — calculated from entries (default 28)
264	
265	**Methods:**
266	- `addEntry(entry)` — adds new cycle entry
267	- `updateEntry(id, entry)` — modifies existing entry
268	- `deleteEntry(id)` — removes entry
269	- `getCurrentCycle()` — returns most recent entry
270	- `getOvulationWindow()` — calculates fertile window based on average
271	
272	**Computed:**
273	- `daysSinceLastPeriod` = today - lastPeriodDate
274	- `nextPeriodEstimate` = lastPeriodDate + averageCycleLength
